Title: Trekking
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/trekking-3
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Ram Dayal Dayal
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I have beautiful experience in Goa trekking.it was wonderful experience of my
  life.i have met lot of friends during trekking.We watched dhudh Sagar ,two parts
  of state one of Karnataka & Goa .we have enjoyed many beautiful beaches such as
  Meera beach,I have completed 25 km walked on beaches.i have met there locally people
  and enjoy local food.it was very delicious.after two days we have entered in jungle.which
  is very deep & fearfully.After crossing the jungle we entered in field & meet local
  people & enjoy the food .I have lot of friends in world.it was great experience
  of life.i have completed 4 trekking in India in different states.
